CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 18, 1953, pg. 7 reads: "The Rev. and Mrs. Cuff Honored - Corinthian Baptist Church honored the Rev. H.S. Cuff on the occasion of his twelfth anniversary as pastor of the church. Mrs. Cuff was also included in this celebration.  The pastor received a suit of clothes, a robe and approximately seven hundred dollars in cash from friends and the departments of the church. Seen here, standing are Mrs. Celester Humphries, Deacon William Lowe.  Seated are the Rev. and Mrs. H.S. Cuff. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Celester Humphries and Deacon William Lowe, standing next to Reverend and Mrs. H.S. Cuff, seated at table with cake, for twelfth anniversary as pastor of Corinthian Baptist Church
